, \"to\": 1308}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whitlock's performance on pommel horse, Team GB's first piece of apparatus, was one of the major positives as the 31-year-old prepares to defend the individual title he won in both Tokyo and Rio this weekend.\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1538, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1330, \"end\": 1338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.279261322939985e-33, \"text\": \"Whitlock\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\"}, {\"begin\": 1370, \"end\": 1377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.999999999782176, \"rank\": 1.87698636824142e-10, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1511, \"end\": 1516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.8978428493707564, \"rank\": 0.113780203781517, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 1521, \"end\": 1524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.011838352177391e-13, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pommel horse\", \"from\": 1356, \"to\": 1368}, {\"ngram\": \"apparatus\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1404}, {\"ngram\": \"the major positives\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1436}, {\"ngram\": \"the 31-year-old prepares\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1464}, {\"ngram\": \"the individual title\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1495}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympics 2024 medal table: Latest count today after Team GB rush on day three Today's Olympic 2024 schedule: Team GB events, medal highlights and how to watch Paris Games Olympics 2024 complete schedule: Date and time for every event Having qualified for that final in third-place, the reigning champion upped his routine's difficulty here and delivered a score of 15.266, the highest of any athlete so far at the Games across both qualifying and the team final.\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 2005, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1592, \"end\": 1599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.999999999782176, \"rank\": 1.87698636824142e-10, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympics 2024 medal table\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1565}, {\"ngram\": \"Latest count\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1579}, {\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\": 1611}, {\"ngram\": \"Today's Olympic 2024 schedule\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1647}, {\"ngram\": \"Team GB events\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1663}, {\"ngram\": \"medal highlights\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1681}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris Games Olympics 2024 complete schedule\", \"from\": 1699, \"to\": 1742}, {\"ngram\": \"every event\", \"from\": 1762, \"to\": 1773}, {\"ngram\": \"third-place\", \"from\": 1809, \"to\": 1820}, {\"ngram\": \"the reigning champion\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1843}, {\"ngram\": \"his routine's difficulty\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 1874}, {\"ngram\": \"a score\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1901}, {\"ngram\": \"any athlete\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 1939}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1950, \"to\": 1959}, {\"ngram\": \"both qualifying\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 1982}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 1987, \"to\": 1995}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can take a lot of confidence from that today because that was the big routine, the highest difficulty, the highest risk-factor, which has the most chance of getting the biggest score,\\\" Whitlock said.\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2209, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2195, \"end\": 2203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.279261322939985e-33, \"text\": \"Whitlock\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2024}, {\"ngram\": \"confidence\", \"from\": 2028, \"to\": 2038}, {\"ngram\": \"the big routine\", \"from\": 2072, \"to\": 2087}, {\"ngram\": \"the highest difficulty\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2111}, {\"ngram\": \"the highest risk-factor\", \"from\": 2113, \"to\": 2136}, {\"ngram\": \"the most chance\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2163}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest score\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2192}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The first piece is always nerve-wracking.\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2253, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The first piece\", \"from\": 2212, \"to\": 2227}, {\"ngram\": \"nerve-wracking\", \"from\": 2238, \"to\": 2252}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It definitely was that.\", \"from\": 2254, \"to\": 2277, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I was mega-pleased that we all got off to a good start.\", \"from\": 2278, \"to\": 2337, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good start\", \"from\": 2324, \"to\": 2336}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are still some errors in there that I can hopefully try and clean up before the final.\", \"from\": 2338, \"to\": 2430, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some errors\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2365}, {\"ngram\": \"the final\", \"from\": 2420, \"to\": 2429}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But overall, I am well happy with that.\\\"\", \"from\": 2431, \"to\": 2471, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The most successful British gymnast of all-time now has just one competition left in his career before heading into retirement after Saturday's final.\", \"from\": 2473, \"to\": 2623, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2493, \"end\": 2500, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.9989970137332667, \"rank\": 0.0009299625060907692, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all-time\", \"from\": 2512, \"to\": 2520}, {\"ngram\": \"just one competition\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2549}, {\"ngram\": \"his career\", \"from\": 2558, \"to\": 2568}, {\"ngram\": \"retirement\", \"from\": 2589, \"to\": 2599}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday's final\", \"from\": 2606, \"to\": 2622}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Qualification was pretty emotional for me, which I was surprised with,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 2625, \"to\": 2707, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Qualification\", \"from\": 2626, \"to\": 2639}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was almost hard to control in the warm-up gym.\", \"from\": 2708, \"to\": 2758, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the warm-up gym\", \"from\": 2742, \"to\": 2757}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I felt a lot of emotion that I have never felt in any competition before.\", \"from\": 2759, \"to\": 2832, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2766, \"to\": 2771}, {\"ngram\": \"emotion\", \"from\": 2775, \"to\": 2782}, {\"ngram\": \"any competition\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 2824}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What helps me is that I can be proud of what I have done.\", \"from\": 2834, \"to\": 2892, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have come out here in my fourth Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 2893, \"to\": 2941, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my fourth Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2917, \"to\": 2940}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am happy to be in this position.\", \"from\": 2942, \"to\": 2976, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this position\", \"from\": 2962, \"to\": 2975}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I wanted to get in a position where I had the potential to gain another title and that's what I have put myself in.\\\"\", \"from\": 2977, \"to\": 3093, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a position\", \"from\": 2996, \"to\": 3006}, {\"ngram\": \"the potential\", \"from\": 3019, \"to\": 3032}, {\"ngram\": \"another title\", \"from\": 3041, \"to\": 3054}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT Have your say... 1 Crime Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping 2 Football Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news 3 UK Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war 4 Lifestyle Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026 Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026 5 Football Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\", \"from\": 3095, \"to\": 3973, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3155, \"end\": 3164, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.9997720588772514, \"rank\": 0.0002257216333972167, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\"}, {\"begin\": 3255, \"end\": 3264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.9997720588772514, \"rank\": 0.0002257216333972167, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"t